---
// BlogPreview.astro — Blog/insights section preview
---

<section class="blog-preview fade-in">
  <h2 class="section-title">Insights & Blog</h2>
  <div class="blog-list">
    <article class="blog-card card-hover">
      <h3>How Machine Learning Improves Earthquake Early Warning</h3>
      <p>Exploring the impact of ensemble ML models on real-time seismic event detection and parameter estimation in Indonesia.</p>
      <a href="#" class="blog-link" aria-label="Read more about ML in EEWS">Read more →</a>
    </article>
    <article class="blog-card card-hover">
      <h3>Seismic Data Processing: Best Practices</h3>
      <p>Key steps and tools for robust seismic data preprocessing, feature extraction, and quality control in research workflows.</p>
      <a href="#" class="blog-link" aria-label="Read more about seismic data processing">Read more →</a>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.blog-preview {
  padding: 3rem 1rem 4rem 1rem;
  background: #f8fafc;
}
.section-title {
  font-size: 2rem;
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
  text-align: center;
}
.blog-list {
  display: grid;
  gap: 2rem;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(320px, 1fr));
  max-width: 900px;
  margin: 0 auto;
}
.blog-card {
  background: #fff;
  border-radius: 1rem;
  box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
  padding: 2rem 2.5rem;
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: 1.2rem;
}
.blog-card h3 {
  color: #6366f1;
  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
}
.blog-link {
  color: #6366f1;
  font-weight: 600;
  text-decoration: none;
  margin-top: auto;
  align-self: flex-end;
  transition: color 0.18s;
}
.blog-link:hover,
.blog-link:focus {
  color: #3730a3;
  text-decoration: underline;
}
@media (max-width: 600px) {
  .blog-card {
    padding: 1.25rem 1rem;
  }
}
</style>
